{"tid":365092,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"另一半有情緒病嘅你地","createTime":"2017-08-19T03:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T02:11:30.000Z","uid":107119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d6575fae75231d88d99dc6d11879620604c1b71","tid":365092,"uid":107119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:24:54.000Z","msg":"我想問下另一半有情緒病嘅你地，拍拖生活過得如何？<br />\n對住有病嘅另一半會唔會覺得好煩，好沮喪，好大壓力？<br />\n平時又點同佢地相處，會唔會有啲嘢唔講得笑，又要俾適當/ 好多嘅空間比佢哋？<br />\n經濟方面又會唔會好大壓力？可能另一半要成日睇醫生？<br />\n<br />\n有無過來人分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c1faff0f261842184e04a94c4f765ae6eab18b","tid":365092,"uid":107119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af7203acd93075decdf2362d94ae5a29686ebad","tid":365092,"uid":107119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:03:33.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"dfbb745d940f5afcd93e7ac54f9aa854ec0aa386","tid":365092,"uid":106734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:08:09.000Z","msg":"我都想知另一半係點頂得順<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔敢再係佢面前放負"},{"pid":"8c6b1469045bd63d0859bb871d3f58039401b763","tid":365092,"uid":13185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:19:10.000Z","msg":"覺得知道另一半有情緒問題 <br />\n都仲走去同佢一齊嘅人<br />\n我真係覺得好佩服 <br />\n因為我自己一定頂唔到人放負"},{"pid":"4a0dc41e456b12ba05d6b97ea0454603c5043b38","tid":365092,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T19:12:07.000Z","msg":"男既勸你唔好搞 遲早俾對方嫌<br />\n女既唔好以為另一半咩都要受 容忍有極限<br />\n過來人"},{"pid":"7da68c1a42149d4c1fa87dbb95751efdaec6ca4b","tid":365092,"uid":94128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T19:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好感激佢喺我最抑鬱既時侯幫我搭線見社工<br />\n好可惜佢既壓力要靠另一個女仔開解 <br />\n一定係我唔好 控制唔到情緒 佢先要揾第二個<br />\n我放負 佢壓力大 揾個女仔 我發現 我嬲 佢要氹 <br />\n於是我疑心越黎越重 佢壓力越黎越大 惡性循環"},{"pid":"60adfd27bc345c8daceea4215a42c756d2c39d19","tid":365092,"uid":107119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T02:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想知另一半係點頂得順<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔敢再係佢面前放負</blockquote><br />\n你有情緒病？分享下？"}]}